estrogen receptor activation from a compound determined to be an estrogen receptor alpha agonist from in vitro estrogenicity results (Feng et al. 2015; Cao et al. 2018; Wang et al. 2018). Studies of laboratory mammals exposed to various forms of estrogen show a subsequent decreased release of kisspeptin from anteroventral periventricular nucleus (AVPV) neurons (Bateman and Patisaul 2008; Homma et al. 2009; Navarro et al. 2009; Patisaul et al. 2009; Ichimura et al. 2015a; Ichimura et al. 2015b).", "timestamp": "Mon Jun 08 16:19:43 +0000 2026"}